customProperties.label: 'transform_cost_table'
customProperties.sql:
'
        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS processed_costs AS
        SELECT
            id,
            month,
            total_cost,
            area,
            total_cost / area as cost_per_area
        FROM costs
        '
